      <title>经合组织警告称世界经济面临贸易和债务风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/world-economy-faces-trade-and-debt-dangers-oecd-warns-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织认为，贸易紧张、战争和债务问题等全球经济风险不断增加，可能威胁到过去几年全球经济“非凡的韧性”。经合组织首席经济学家阿尔瓦罗·佩雷拉详细介绍了该组织最新的全球经济展望。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/world-economy-faces-trade-and-debt-dangers-oecd-warns-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人们正在努力保持减肥效果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/people-are-fighting-to-keep-their-weight-loss-shots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着需求和成本的飙升，保险公司越来越多地取消对 Ozempic 和 Wegovy 等药物的承保。我们采访了患者，了解他们为保留药物而做出的努力。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-04/people-are-fighting-to-keep-their-weight-loss-shots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 11:01:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普和哈维尔·米莱为何在紧缩政策上分歧巨大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/why-donald-trump-and-javier-milei-are-worlds-apart-on-austerity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从发型、社交媒体和针对对手的策略来看，唐纳德·特朗普和阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱伊似乎是一丘之貉。但风格和实质是两码事。]]></description>
